pan style=\"color: gold;\">32,675 至 52,578</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">仇恨</span></strong><br />\n大半年打壓知識份子<br />\n當中不少醫護人士被打拉射告<br />\n而家就有事求人<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">無保障</span></strong><br />\n封關只係其中一樣<br />\n大劣病人根本唔守規矩<br />\n人地支那都識立法保護醫護人員<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20200130%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html&d=7U4Tv3rjd6zAHDU%2B6Dwik%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=f6f67b54\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20200130/mobile/bkn-20200130111932894-0130_00952_001.html</a><br />\n而且不幸染病死左只有50萬賠償真係on9<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">對應解決方法</span></span><br />\n1.cut 狗隊資源及一半人工<br />\n提升醫護界薪金2倍<br />\n<br />\n2.答應五大訴求，追究警暴，放義士，<br />\n高官問責，實行雙普選，減仇恨<br />\n<br />\n3.提升醫護個人裝備，立法限制病人行為<br />\n立即全面封關，賠償額提升到500萬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本你做少一樣，醫護都唔會開工</span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"15fcf6466c5bb6d1ab1313b77b3593bad507e8cc","tid":1853643,"uid":189650,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:40:23.000Z","msg":"超過6,700宣布會罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7142846376792a3e8ec54ffc6d70c8636ff1c3d3","tid":1853643,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:40:32.000Z","msg":"工會冇呼籲大家請病假， <br />\n大家已經嬲到自發組織請病假。"},{"pid":"58fff30988aa885fc97a1f60286a85f5475fc4ef","tid":1853643,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"聽日開會員大會"},{"pid":"b5b47b0f894453da948b278ffb30cc7353c707ea","tid":1853643,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T06:45:02.000Z","msg":"一日唔封關， 一日都會唔夠資源。"},{"pid":"118e